Data from Freedland J. and Rieke F, 2022

1. Download data from: https://datadryad.org/stash/share/cX_5w1l_NAtMlP-tjO8CKRwZZQIgjS0K9GcXbvGBca4 to the macaque_movie folder.
2. Preprocess mat files using scripts/process_mats.m (make sure to change the export path in the script).
3. Export movie mats using scripts/build_movie_mats.m (make sure to change the export path in the script).
4. Build PyTorch tensor using scripts/build_tensors.py (make sure to pass root argument of project).
